- make sure you have `java`

  ``` shell
  java -version
  ```

- if you don\'t have it

  ``` shell
  sudo apt update
  sudo apt install default-jre
  ```

- download soapui from <https://www.soapui.org/downloads/thank-you-for-downloading-soapui/>

- install by following insatllation wizard
